{"tid":1551248,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9.8 美領Twitter繼續鼓勵為港發聲美議員/官員 （記錄用）","createTime":"2019-09-08T02:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:11:01.000Z","uid":296902,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"241b676eb93e6c6fecffa9d204088fa1ecf03ca8","tid":1551248,"uid":296902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"9.8 去美領，希望各位繼續寫字牌鼓勵曾經為香港發聲的美國國會議員，請佢地繼續支持香港人權與民主法案。亦可twitter同佢地交流一下，把集會照片及報導推發給相關議員，多謝佢地，或者提議下制裁名單同點增強法案內容。 大家要繼續努力同各位美國有心人講，法案一定要過同要正式開始制裁d官員，吾要只系用來做樣，如果唔係香港政府只會繼續欺壓香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n如果系美國人巴絲，吾好怕醜，打電話或者send電郵給你地議員同佢講你想佢支持法案啦。美國議員都系要為人民同選票服務，佢幫你打工噶，記得關心下佢這方面工作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下系整理名單（付twitter賬號），歡迎補充：<br />\n</strong><br />\nD = 民主黨 <br />\nR = 共和黨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>SENATE 參議院方面：<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<strong>在Senate提出香港民主法案之議員： </strong><br />\n- Marco Rubio (R-Florida) [url]@marcorubio [/url]<br />\n- Ben Cardin (D-Maryland) [url]@SenatorCardin[/url] <br />\n- Jim Risch (R-Idaho), Chairman of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee [url]@SenatorRisch [/url]<br />\n- Bob Menendez (D-New Jersey), Ranking Member of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee [url]@SenatorMenendez[/url]<br />\n  <br />\n<strong>贊助議案之Senate議員名單 </strong><br />\n- Angus King (I-Maine), [url]@SenAngusKing [/url]<br />\n- Josh Hawley (R-Missouri), [url]@JohnAHawley [/url]<br />\n- Ed Markey (D-Massachussets) [url]@SenMarkey [/url]<br />\n- Tom Cotton (R-Arkansas), [url]@SenTomCotton [/url]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>曾表態支持香港或議案之Senator </strong><br />\n- Mitch McConnell  (R-Washington) 共和黨參議院領導 [url]@senatemajldr [/url] <br />\n- Chuck Schmer (D-NY) 民主黨參議院領導 [url]@SenSchumer [/url]<br />\n- Ted Cruz (R-Texas) [url]@tedcruz [/url]<br />\n- Mitt Romney (R-Utah) [url]@SenatorRomney[/url], [url]@MittRomney [/url]<br />\n- Rick Scott (R-Florida) [url]@SenRickScott[/url] <br />\n- Cory Gardner (R-Colorado) [url]@SenCoryGardner[/url] 批評警察暴力 <br />\n- Elizabeth Warren (D- Massachussets) [url]@SenWarren[/url] 有機會成為民主黨總統候選人<br />\n- Bernie Sanders (D-Vermont) [url]@BernieSanders [/url]有機會成為民主黨總統候選人<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>HOUSE 眾議院方面：</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>House提出及贊助香港民主法案議員 </strong><br />\n- Christopher &ldquo;Chris&rdquo; Smith (R-NJ) [url]@RepChrisSmith[/url] <br />\n- Jim McGovern (D-MA) [url]@RepMcGovern [/url]<br />\n- Tom Suozzi (D-NY) [url]@RepTomSuozzi [/url]<br />\n- Scott Perry (R-PA) [url]@RepScottPerry [/url]<br />\n- Brad Sherman (D-CA) [url]@BradSherman [/url]<br />\n- Ted Yoho (R-FL) [url]@RepTedYoho [/url]<br />\n- Brian Fitzpatrick (R-PA)  [url]@RepBrianFitz [/url]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>曾表態支持香港或議案之House Rep </strong><br />\n- Nancy Pelosi (D-CA) [url]@SpeakerPelosi [/url]<br />\n- Kevin McCarthy (R-CA)), House Minority Leader [url]@GOPLeader [/url]<br />\n- Steny Hoyer (D-MD), House Majority Leader [url]@LeaderHoyer[/url]<br />\n歡迎各位手足補完，之後樓主亦會陸續增加官員及留下相關言論作記錄"},{"pid":"98ef6c78313770cde2dfeabed9a9382131a74a2a","tid":1551248,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:16:53.000Z","msg":"有冇啲係反對嘅議員？"},{"pid":"fdafc622be302a150813c5b7175501b04c7566fa","tid":1551248,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:18:11.000Z","msg":"(極緊急)(全美直播) 唱美國國歌必須注意的三件事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2bdb1c0cdd5f4f874cbfe4b805f7f6032bf47a03","tid":1551248,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MVQn2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MVQn2p.jpg&h=89a5dfdb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ts679Hq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTs679Hq.png&h=7aa9bc92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoadkO5.jpg\" data-thum